Package: docstyle
Title: Style-as-Code for Scientific Publishing
Version: 0.19.0
Authors@R:
    person("Douglas", "Manuel", , "dmanuel@ohri.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate Word, PDF, HTML, and PowerPoint assets from a single
    CSS + YAML configuration. Provides round-trip collaboration support for
    scientific publishing workflows, allowing reviewer edits from Word to be
    imported back into Quarto/Markdown source files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
